    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Wed Jan 22 2020 11:10:19 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><h1 id="jConsole监控远程Linux服务器分析JVM"><a href="#jConsole监控远程Linux服务器分析JVM" class="headerlink" title="jConsole监控远程Linux服务器分析JVM"></a>jConsole监控远程Linux服务器分析JVM</h1><p>尝试过很多的方法都出现本地jConsole连接不上远程服务器</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="解决方式"><a href="#解决方式" class="headerlink" title="解决方式"></a>解决方式</h2><h2 id="一、免鉴权方式（简单，有安全问题不推荐）"><a href="#一、免鉴权方式（简单，有安全问题不推荐）" class="headerlink" title="一、免鉴权方式（简单，有安全问题不推荐）"></a>一、免鉴权方式（简单，有安全问题不推荐）</h2><h3 id="1-在配置文件-vim-etc-profile"><a href="#1-在配置文件-vim-etc-profile" class="headerlink" title="1.在配置文件 vim /etc/profile"></a>1.在配置文件 vim /etc/profile</h3><p>新增export JAVA_OPTS=’-Djava.rmi.server.hostname=远程服务器ip</p><p>-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote -Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.port=8083</p><p>-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.rmi.port=8083</p><p>-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.authenticate=false</p><p>-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.ssl=false’</p><p>远程服务器打开 配置的端口（这儿是8083）</p><h4 id="2-刷新配置文件：source-etc-profile"><a href="#2-刷新配置文件：source-etc-profile" class="headerlink" title="2.刷新配置文件：source /etc/profile"></a>2.刷新配置文件：source /etc/profile</h4><h4 id="3-启动文件：-java-JAVA-OPTS-jar-jar包名"><a href="#3-启动文件：-java-JAVA-OPTS-jar-jar包名" class="headerlink" title="3.启动文件： java  $JAVA_OPTS  -jar  jar包名"></a>3.启动文件： java $JAVA_OPTS -jar jar包名</h4><p>nohup java $JAVA_OPTS -jar jar包名 &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp; 后台启动</p><h4 id="4-netstat-tunlp-查看所有端口中有无配置好的端口"><a href="#4-netstat-tunlp-查看所有端口中有无配置好的端口" class="headerlink" title="4.netstat   -tunlp 查看所有端口中有无配置好的端口"></a>4.netstat -tunlp 查看所有端口中有无配置好的端口</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tcp        <span class="number">0</span>      <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:<span class="number">8080</span>            <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:*               LISTEN      <span class="number">16484</span>/nginx: master </span><br><span class="line">tcp        <span class="number">0</span>      <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:<span class="number">80</span>              <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:*               LISTEN      <span class="number">16484</span>/nginx: master </span><br><span class="line">tcp        <span class="number">0</span>      <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:<span class="number">8082</span>            <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:*               LISTEN      <span class="number">1098</span>/java           </span><br><span class="line">tcp        <span class="number">0</span>      <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:<span class="number">8083</span>            <span class="number">0.0</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.0</span>:*               LISTEN      <span class="number">1098</span>/java</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="5-本地命令行输入jConsole"><a href="#5-本地命令行输入jConsole" class="headerlink" title="5.本地命令行输入jConsole"></a>5.本地命令行输入jConsole</h4><h4 id="6-建立远程连接，因为-Dcom-sun-management-jmxremote-authenticate-false-所有不用鉴权。不用账号和密码直接连接"><a href="#6-建立远程连接，因为-Dcom-sun-management-jmxremote-authenticate-false-所有不用鉴权。不用账号和密码直接连接" class="headerlink" title="6.建立远程连接，因为-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.authenticate=false  所有不用鉴权。不用账号和密码直接连接"></a>6.建立远程连接，因为-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.authenticate=false 所有不用鉴权。不用账号和密码直接连接</h4><p>建议开启鉴权-Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.authenticate=true</p><h2 id="二、鉴权方式"><a href="#二、鉴权方式" class="headerlink" title="二、鉴权方式"></a>二、鉴权方式</h2><h4 id="1-找到你的jvm路径"><a href="#1-找到你的jvm路径" class="headerlink" title="1.找到你的jvm路径"></a>1.找到你的jvm路径</h4><p>比如：cd /usr/lib/jvm/java-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.181-3.b13.el7_5.x86_64/jre/lib/management/</p><h4 id="2-复制一份密码文件并且赋予写的权限"><a href="#2-复制一份密码文件并且赋予写的权限" class="headerlink" title="2.复制一份密码文件并且赋予写的权限"></a>2.复制一份密码文件并且赋予写的权限</h4><p>cp jmxremote.password.template jmxremote.password</p><p>chomd +w jmxremote.password</p><h4 id="3-vim-jmxremote-password-将后面monitorRole-、controlRole注释放开"><a href="#3-vim-jmxremote-password-将后面monitorRole-、controlRole注释放开" class="headerlink" title="3.vim  jmxremote.password  将后面monitorRole 、controlRole注释放开"></a>3.vim jmxremote.password 将后面monitorRole 、controlRole注释放开</h4><p>monitorRole 、controlRole是定义在jmxremote.access中的权限角色，前者只可读，后者可读可写</p><h4 id="4-赋予文件权限：chmod-600-jmxremote-password-jmxremote-access"><a href="#4-赋予文件权限：chmod-600-jmxremote-password-jmxremote-access" class="headerlink" title="4.赋予文件权限：chmod  600  jmxremote.password  jmxremote.access"></a>4.赋予文件权限：chmod 600 jmxremote.password jmxremote.access</h4><h4 id="5-启动然后继续前面一样的操作"><a href="#5-启动然后继续前面一样的操作" class="headerlink" title="5.启动然后继续前面一样的操作"></a>5.启动然后继续前面一样的操作</h4><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
    
